SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from VIN_MONTH_CODE_MASTER M where M.Mon_cd=substr(':1',9,1) AND (M.MON_SR<=to_char(sysdate,'MM') and to_char(sysdate,'YYYY')>=(SELECT SUBSTR(PLN_DAT,1,4) FROM PRD005 WHERE EF_TYP=SUBSTR(':1',1,11) AND SHA_NO=SUBSTR(':1',12,17))) or to_char(sysdate,'YYYY')>(SELECT SUBSTR(PLN_DAT,1,4) FROM PRD005 WHERE EF_TYP=SUBSTR(':1',1,11) AND SHA_NO=SUBSTR(':1',12,17)) or substr(':1',9,1)='0'
